Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（小雪）自分の好みで\N選んでしまった
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.82,0:08:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（ミナト）はい
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.83,0:08:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}え？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（ミナト）あげる
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（小雪）え？　ん…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.00,0:08:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}こゆんちゃん 誕生日おめでとう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.83,0:08:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}え？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.34,0:08:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}え？　え？　え？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.05,0:08:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}そんな… え？　いや…\Nえ？　え？　ん？　あ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.42,0:08:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}ええ？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.97,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}はあ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}ふ～ん
