Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}ニャニャニャニャーだ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.19,0:11:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}（ヨータ）はははっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（月子）わぁ～ 安曇(あずみ)さんだ～！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:42.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}でも…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.53,0:11:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}安曇さんって…
