Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.75,0:11:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}（月子）思ってた感じと違う
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.79,0:11:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}（美姫）あっ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\c&Hffffff&}はじめまして！\N美姫っていいまーす
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.17,0:11:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}カ…
